@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy | Green Oasis Resort — Leading Casino Resort Platform";
    var site = SiteSettingsOptions.Value;
}

<section class="page-header page-header-image" style="background-image: url('/images/hero.jpg');" aria-label="Privacy Policy">
    <div class="page-header-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="container page-header-content">
        <span class="hero-badge">Legal</span>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>How we collect, use, and protect your information in compliance with GDPR.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section" aria-labelledby="privacy-heading">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content-card">
            <p class="policy-updated"><em>Last updated: June 12, 2026</em></p>

            <h2 id="privacy-heading">1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>
                Green Oasis Resort ("we", "our", or "us"), operating at @site.Domain, is committed to protecting your privacy.
                This policy explains how we handle personal information when you visit our website or contact us, in full
                accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and applicable European privacy law.
            </p>

            <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We may collect the following information:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Contact details:</strong> Name, email address, and phone number when you submit a form.</li>
                <li><strong>Message content:</strong> Subject and body of enquiries you send us.</li>
                <li><strong>Technical data:</strong> IP address, browser type, and basic usage data through standard server logs.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use collected information to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Respond to your questions, enquiries, and reservation requests</li>
                <li>Improve our website and hospitality services</li>
                <li>Comply with legal obligations under EU and international law</li>
                <li>Send updates only where you have expressly agreed to receive them</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
            <p>
                We process personal data based on your consent (when you submit a contact form), our legitimate interest
                in operating and improving the platform, and compliance with applicable legal obligations.
            </p>

            <h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
            <p>
                We do not sell your personal information. We may share data with trusted service providers who assist us
                in operating the website, subject to strict confidentiality agreements and only as required to deliver
                our services to you.
            </p>

            <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
            <p>
                We retain personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes described in this policy
                or as required by applicable law. Enquiry data is typically retained for up to 24 months.
            </p>

            <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
            <p>Under the GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
                <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
                <li>Object to or restrict certain types of processing</li>
                <li>Withdraw consent at any time where processing is based on consent</li>
                <li>Lodge a complaint with your local data protection authority</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>8. Cookies</h2>
            <p>
                Our website uses only essential cookies required for basic functionality and security. We do not use
                advertising or tracking cookies. You can manage and disable cookies through your browser settings.
            </p>

            <h2>9. Security</h2>
            <p>
                We employ industry-standard technical and organisational measures — including SSL encryption, secure
                server infrastructure, and access controls — to protect your information from unauthorised access,
                disclosure, or loss.
            </p>

            <h2>10. Responsible Gaming &amp; Age Verification</h2>
            <p>
                Green Oasis Resort is a casino resort platform intended exclusively for adults aged 18 and over. By using
                our platform, you confirm you are of legal age in your jurisdiction. We are committed to responsible
                entertainment practices and do not promote gambling to vulnerable persons or minors. If you have concerns
                about gambling, please contact <a href="https://www.begambleaware.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--gold-primary);">BeGambleAware.org</a>.
            </p>

            <h2>11. Contact</h2>
            <p>
                For privacy questions or to exercise your rights, please email <strong>@site.PrivacyEmail</strong> or write to us at:
                1 Avenue de la Mer, Monaco, MC 98000.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
